    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we didn't see that many, you know, when there was an inspection, so that was-- everybody had to disappear in the barracks.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the blockalteste had to salute.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] and then they walked through the block.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if there was a speck of dust on the mud floor, somebody would get it.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So that's about how it worked.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Eva, we're going to take a break.",
